<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.9.8">
<l>kuṭaittiṟal maṉṉava ṉāyoru kālkuraṅ kaippaṭai yāmalai yālkaṭalai</l>
<l>yaṭaittava ṉentaipi rāṉati ṭammaṇi māṭaṅkaḷ cūḻntaḻa kāyakacci</l>
<l>viṭaittiṟal villavaṉ neṉmeli yilveru vacceru vēlvalaṅ kaippiṭitta</l>
<l>paṭaittiṟal pallavar kōṉpaṇin tapara mēccura viṇṇaka ramatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In fair Kacci encircled by jeweled mansions, the place of our father,</l>
<l rend="indent">the lord, the one who once,</l>
<l>As a valiant king with an umbrella, blocked the sea with mountains</l>
<l rend="indent">[using] monkeys as [his] army,</l>
<l>Is Paramēccura Viṇṇakaram where bowed the king of the Pallavas,</l>
<l rend="indent">armed and valiant,</l>
<l>Who bore in the right hand the battle spear so that, in Neṉmeli</l>
<l rend="indent">the bow-bearer, as valiant as a bull, feared [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
